Yes, that plan works well for me. I can be there a little before noon so we have enough time to get settled and go over the schedule.
If you want, send the address again since I may come from a different direction than usual.
I also think it makes sense to keep the agenda simple and leave room for any changes once everyone arrives.
For food, something light is probably easiest, and I can bring fruit, sparkling water, and a small dessert.
If weather shifts, we can stay indoors and still cover everything we need without changing much.

Marriot

Previous stay recognition for eligible guests

Ends Tomorrow

A hospitality follow-up tied to your recent stay

Because you stayed at a Marriot Hotel or a Marriot partnered hotel within the past year, you may receive one 2-pillow luxury cooling set per household, provided at no charge. After you complete a brief questionnaire, you can also claim a 2-night stay at select locations at no charge. You will not be billed for the pillows or the qualifying stay nights.

View Pillows + 2 Night Stay

Included for eligible households

One 2-pillow set, prepared for shipment after questionnaire completion.

Stay access after the survey

A 2-night stay at select locations may be claimed after the brief response form is finished.

Why you are seeing this

This is available to you because you stayed with Marriot or a partner location within the last year.

Current allocation

Total pillow allocation is 500 sets for this program window. Participation period ends Tomorrow.

The questionnaire is brief and helps confirm shipping details. Stay dates and participating locations are based on program scheduling, and quantities are determined by program allocation.

What stands out about this cooling pillow pair

1. Cooling fabrics help reduce heat build-up around the head and neck.

2. A smooth outer cover adds a clean, hotel-style finish.

3. The fill is designed to support common sleep positions with gentle cushioning.

4. Breathable construction encourages steadier airflow through the night.

5. Balanced loft helps the pillows keep a full shape while staying comfortable.

6. Having a matching set makes it simple to refresh both sides of the bed at once.

Thank you for staying at a Marriot Hotel. Your participation helps us extend this household shipping and stay program to prior guests in a clear and orderly way.

 

I think Saturday would be better than Friday because it gives us more time to get organized and avoids feeling rushed after work.
We can start early, sort out the materials, and then take a break in the afternoon if things run long.
I looked over the notes you sent and the second outline seems clearer, especially for the timeline and who is handling each part.
I can draft the summary before I arrive so we are not building everything from the start.
Let me know if anyone has dietary restrictions and whether we should bring extra chairs or just keep the group smaller.

